<br>
1) I'd like a bowl of Chicken Noodle soup please.<br>
<br>
or <br>
<br>
2) I'd like the half soup half salad with Chicken Noodle soup and the whatever I'm in the mood for salad.<br>
<br>
Sometimes I vary the soup.  And in the summer sometimes I go crazy and order an Iced Tea.<br>
<br>
I guess being a creature of habit makes my life boring, but at least my order is easy since I get practically the same thing ever time.<br>
